name: An Ode to Time
description:
I have come to an agreement with time, mostly with the present moment. For so long I have neglect it, photography serves me as a medium to appreciate where I am, here and now. Never forgetting that life is constantly in movement, changing. Here we are, next second we don't know. To the buyer of this piece, I will gift a print and reveal the special location of this place.

Thank you to my friend Braulio Lam for letting me use his music.
Song: Kinetic 1
